Keywords
Variable Declarations and Control Flow:
let, mut, if, else, while, for, loop, match, return, break, continue
Function and Struct Definitions:
fn, struct, enum, trait, impl
Ownership and Borrowing:
move, ref, mut
Data Types and Modifiers:
bool, char, i8, i16, i32, i64, u8, u16, u32, u64, f32, f64, str
Concurrency and Error Handling:
async, await, Result, Ok, Err
Regular Expressions:
Identifiers: [a-zA-Z_][a-zA-Z0-9_]*
Numbers:
Regular expression for integers: [-+]?[0-9]+
Regular expression for floating-point numbers: [-+]?[0-9]*\.[0-9]+
Operators and Punctuation: [+\-*/=<>!%^&|]+
String Literals: \"(\\.|[^\"])*\"
Whitespace: \s+
Comments:
Regular expression for single-line comments: //.*
Regular expression for multi-line comments: /\*(.|[\r\n])*?\*/
